Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來到你這兒之後我挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.86,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz27.89\c&H53565A&\fn方正静蕾简体\pos(838,458)}新田收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:08.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你為我做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:12.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在是無法當面跟你說我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也不想回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕你會問東問西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:20.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我必須要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不聽她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她就會扭斷我的脖子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經沒什麼好留戀的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 新田
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
