Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:16.71,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:21.51,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:24.32,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:27.13,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.49,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.26,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:39.69,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:45.94,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
