Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:13.65,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(960,0)\an8}第八話 然後雛一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說雛在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這個城市好像還挺和平的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我送外賣回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子啊 沒想到你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得你好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:45.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警備主任 斑 斑 斑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫斑鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,問也是白問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以別在這裡動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話儘量在僻靜的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔阿姨 謝謝你們這段時間的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我活得很充實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是不是搞錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你沒有回來 我們就把你認定為戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來調查雛的行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至於你嘛 喜歡的話你就在這生活唄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就這樣對待我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:23.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在還來調查雛 是要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:31.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她很容易暴走 所以她被廢棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然把你給派來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們知道你沒能除掉她
