Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這比小朋友守則的要求還低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「是」越多的話就越好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有認真考慮過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊 這可是那個雛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先把工作完成再回去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一個普通人 上司這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:06.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 以前命令我們的時候那麼牛逼哄哄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她之前暴走摧毀城市的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,項圈也被她弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是她反抗我的話 我可應付不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:14.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在靠什麼生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個叫新田的撿到了她 現在跟他在一塊生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是成了他女兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:27.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等不懼死亡的聖人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她腳好像受傷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是被新田抱起來轉圈圈 撞到了牆上骨折的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個最強生物到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直沒法構想新田的人物形象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再逃避現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 這上邊的都會是「否」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 全都選「否」然後交上去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:56.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請你認真工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本人還是非常了解她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.65,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz18.04\pos(750,398)\c&H242424&}紅燈停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說這一條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:04.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不給她下命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她就會把路上的車全部掀翻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,或者把紅綠燈給掰爛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 她居然在紅燈時停下了
