Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 這才不是雛
