Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.31,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,404)\c&H353535&}會和別人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:36.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是一群量身訂製的小混混啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於等到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會把他們給踢飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對 殺了他們 殺了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:54.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雨也下大了 咱們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是來幹什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 剛才那個說到底也只是初級篇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們在這兒測試高級篇的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是想選個「否」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們就先來個這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.68,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H242424&\pos(834,442)}關愛動物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種狀況還是比較少的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊的寵物商店買隻狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就把它當做是棄狗放在雛的回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.74,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正静蕾简体\bord2\c&H2C2929&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(838,708)}棄狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:37.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊 是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:41.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後她還去偷了傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於看到了她的本性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 難道說 難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她居然會關愛動物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狗也無家可歸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾經經歷過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:17.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛比我想像的要成長了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我說的是那狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能買下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是餐飲店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.01,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs100\c&H2B2B2B&\pos(1316,372)\frz2.381}附加條款
