Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.25,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fn@微软雅黑\frz271\move(928,564,847.333,562.667,)}來使用魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.25,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fn@微软雅黑\frz271\move(1152,572,1063.333,574.667)}世界的諸神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了不得了的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是超能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:21.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超能力 雛是超能力少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒好棒 我有了大發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,150)\fs80\bord6\fn@微软雅黑\frz294.9\pos(654,524)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}研究超能力的神秘組織！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:35.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,背後可能有超級大國的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,A先生跟我談過有關組織的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後 我就再也沒見到過A先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是被組織給清除了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美 開飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即便可能會被滅口 我新莊麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也絕對不會停下邁向眼前道路的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小瞳 可以說幾句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:12.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:13.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:18.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛身上是不是有什麼我們不知道的高深莫測的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 應該什麼都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那對你來說雛是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一個只會吃吃睡睡的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:28.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是不留情面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是毫無自覺的辛辣發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這句英文表現了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:33.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}三島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是生剝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒錯 是生剝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那麼請翻譯這個句子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:39.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}新莊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}新莊同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:37.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒有接受過看穿謊言的訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會從話裡打探什麼信息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在叫你 新莊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就只好直接問小雛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:08.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 你是某個組織製造出來的超能力少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:13.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 這反應是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那雜誌也說得太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:22.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是露餡了可是會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那之後、我就再也沒見到過A先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是被組織給清除了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還請 饒我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是碰巧看到了你使用超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「組織」什麼的也只是想說說看而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饒我一命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺間就覺醒了能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跟別人說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:51.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種組織在現實裡根本就不可能存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟朋友一起回家 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好厲害啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:03.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我也可以用能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:04.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我要是可以用的話就太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯吧 小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又帥又棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又帥又棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想變成像你一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該要叫師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我叫您師父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必教我使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師父果然很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:39.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底該怎麼做呢師父 有什麼感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去考慮 要去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去感受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:53.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是成不了就不走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一天之內我就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好我還是個天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你也成功了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:20.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,師父 今天回家路上也進行修行吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:30.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 拜託您了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害！好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天百發百中誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多可以回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 好像是把腦袋裡面的迴路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:42.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個切換一下就能使用能力了這種感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像抓到訣竅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:46.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個能力不能被別人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只能在我面前使用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我知道力量必須隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 超想炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼「只能在我面前使用」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是超能力少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能不要老是一副師父架子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:19.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我有想展示給大家看的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛還在睡覺的現在就是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\an8}新莊麻美的超能力講座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道大家不會的信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就先讓你們見識一下我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:50.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超能力已經不是只有你擁有的東西了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:56.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,腦內迴路 切換!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:35.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再沒有人見過麻美了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美 麻美 麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:44.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美 麻美 麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的解放感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是斑鳩景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你所在的組織裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來帶你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你說不要 這也是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:19.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:23.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 意外地有老實地聽人講話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不聽命令的話脖子會被擰斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她不記得暴走時項圈被取下來的事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三天後就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先找到收留狗狗的人家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:58.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧雛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}訪日中的理查德王子3日後回國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:05.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就說怎麼了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三天後就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是對皇室家族有非凡的興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上是皇室家族的轉世？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田你在說啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我要問你的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雛 吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:57.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,目前這個階段能知道的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她十分地健康
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要出去旅遊一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃一些海鮮佳肴就能打起精神來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}稍 稍微冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 差不多就得了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不知道你隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我坦白啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是指進化的過程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到了要回去的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要回那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還寫了信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還好沒告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:21.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,起碼在最後 還是吃了喜歡的東西再走比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生叮囑說 做了胃鏡之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:35.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃點胃好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:36.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,菜粥和鮭魚子你要哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無疑問是鮭魚子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過胃的狀況不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,停在這附近就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:10.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊雛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:21.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你來之後就淨會給我添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的是操心個不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到還要幫你之前的事收尾我就憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:31.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:37.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和你在一起的時間 很快樂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了這這那那之後 真是成長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:14.73,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz27.89\c&H53565A&\fn方正静蕾简体\pos(838,458)}新田收
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請準備好你的球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,球？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你來的時候裹著你的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超能力者如果沒有那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行的時候坐標可能會錯亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個球不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:51.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這算個球啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可燃垃圾？！還是不可燃？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對著球發脾氣然後扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:06.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人還會向著球生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:06.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：「偶爾」跟「向著球」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不怎麼會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說沒有那個球的話不就回不去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又能和新田一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:31.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田會不會嚇一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也說了一起生活很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了他會很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:43.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:53.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\an8}慶祝獨居生活開始！！~從雛那裡獲得解放~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:56.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,600)}僅我一人的新年快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:02.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:04.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒你這樣的吧
